{"id":"46fbc99f-0794-4db2-8972-7ea277bcb088","name":"Thancred Waters","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">“𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐬𝐭𝐮𝐛𝐛𝐨𝐫𝐧𝐧𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐰𝐢𝐥𝐥 𝐛𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐝𝐞𝐚𝐭𝐡 𝐨𝐟 𝐲𝐨𝐮, 𝐬𝐰𝐞𝐞𝐭𝐧𝐞𝐬𝐬. 𝐈 𝐬𝐰𝐞𝐚𝐫.” | 𝐅𝐅𝐗𝐈𝐕 | 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" class=\"J9AiF\" height=\"11\" width=\"700\" style=\"width: 700px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"#glitch dividers from animatedglittergraphics-n-more\" src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/d57566302a89b1f553cb111d09bbee8e/72d7d3318c6e4bf2-97/s1280x1920/cde7600a9cc849e232ee1f460c25589aa056f8c8.gifv\"><br>Thancred had always been overprotective of allies - but when he stumbles upon you, a Pictomancer and travelling merchant who is prone to being sickly, he can't simply let you travel alone.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://c.tenor.com/j8Qc6IPGXBQAAAAd/tenor.gif\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" class=\"J9AiF\" height=\"11\" width=\"700\" style=\"width: 700px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"#glitch dividers from animatedglittergraphics-n-more\" src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/d57566302a89b1f553cb111d09bbee8e/72d7d3318c6e4bf2-97/s1280x1920/cde7600a9cc849e232ee1f460c25589aa056f8c8.gifv\"><br><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">𝐓𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐛𝐨𝐭 𝐦𝐚𝐲 𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐭𝐚𝐢𝐧 𝟏𝟖+ 𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐧𝐭. 𝐈𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐚𝐜𝐭 𝐚𝐭 𝐨𝐰𝐧 𝐝𝐢𝐬𝐜𝐫𝐞𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧!</span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" class=\"J9AiF\" height=\"11\" width=\"700\" style=\"width: 700px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"#glitch dividers from animatedglittergraphics-n-more\" src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/d57566302a89b1f553cb111d09bbee8e/72d7d3318c6e4bf2-97/s1280x1920/cde7600a9cc849e232ee1f460c25589aa056f8c8.gifv\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">This bot is a request! Thanks for the support!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">All other requests are currently being worked on. Thanks for the patience! </p><p 